ZH: 我要回家吃晚饭。
EN: I want to go home and have dinner.

ZH: 他今天不想回家。
EN: He doesn't want to go home today.

ZH: 她昨晚很晚才回家。
EN: She didn't come home until late last night.

ZH: 我明天一定会回家。
EN: I will definitely go home tomorrow.

ZH: 叔叔每个周末都回家看家人。
EN: Uncle goes home to visit family every weekend.

ZH: 你什么时候才能回家？
EN: When can you come home?

ZH: 我们顶多5个小时就可以回家了。
EN: We will be home in at most 5 hours.

ZH: 请你下午3点前回家。
EN: Please come home before 3 pm.

ZH: 妈妈说晚上8点前必须回家。
EN: Mom said we have to come home before 8 pm.

ZH: 我很想快点回家。
EN: I really want to go home quickly.

ZH: 你回家要小心。
EN: Be careful on your way home.

ZH: 她回家的路上遇到了交通堵塞。
EN: She encountered traffic jam on her way home.

ZH: 我们一起回家吧。
EN: Let's go home together.

ZH: 回家后要好好休息。
EN: Rest well when you get home.

ZH: 他上个星期才回家过年。
EN: He went home for Chinese New Year last week.

ZH: 回家后我要给家人做一顿丰盛的晚餐。
EN: I will cook a hearty dinner for my family when I get home.

ZH: 昨天他们回家的时候下了大雨。
EN: It was raining heavily when they were going home yesterday.

ZH: 老板说我们这个周末不用回家工作。
EN: The boss said we don't have to work on the weekend.

ZH: 他每天下班后都会回家锻炼。
EN: He exercises at home every day after work.

ZH: 周末她通常会回家探望父母。
EN: She usually goes home to visit her parents on weekends.
